Re: FluxBB 1.5.11 released

   Hi,

   I'm really sorry Franz, but, for the moment, I won't update my forum to
   1.5.11. This means I won't update the Mod Installer plugin and
   associated mods like VSABR.
   In the names of those who participated in this update, Visman appears
   and I thought some of these changes had been taken into account, but
   the parser did not change by an iota between 1.5.10 and 1.5.11, which
   means, for example, that the "create_function()" (obsolete since PHP
   7.2) have not been replaced by "function() {...}.
   At my age, I am in favour of the slightest effort, which means that I
   absolutely do not want to have to reintegrate the modifications of
   Visman's parser (which I thank very much) after having updated to
   1.5.11.
   I am the only developer of Wampserver and I already have a lot of work
   to do with it, so I try not to change my workload.

   With kind regards.
